// =============================================================================
// core.math.foundations — meta-classifier-relative foundation packages
// =============================================================================
//
// Companion to `core.math.frameworks.*`. Where `frameworks` exposes
// trusted-axiom packages cited from external mathematical literature
// (Lurie HTT, Schreiber DCCT, Connes-Chamseddine, Petz, Arnold,
// Baez-Dolan, OWL 2 FS, Diakrisis), `foundations` exposes the
// *meta-classifier-relative* layer:
//
//   • `self_recognition` — VVA Phase 5 architectural theorems:
//                          Verum's own kernel rules (K-Refine /
//                          K-Adj-Unit / K-Adj-Counit / K-Pos / K-Norm
//                          / K-FwAx) re-stated as @theorem and
//                          cross-validated against the Diakrisis
//                          corpus citation. The deepest test of
//                          foundation-neutral hosting: Verum's
//                          verification stack proves the architectural
//                          invariants that justify itself.
//
// Future entries (per VVA conveyor):
//   • metaclassification — already lives at `core.math.frameworks.diakrisis`
//   • biadjunction       — already at `core.math.frameworks.diakrisis_biadjunction`
//   • stack_model_axioms — already at `core.math.frameworks.diakrisis_stack_model`
//   • universe_ascent    — pending (#171 K-Universe-Ascent V1)
// =============================================================================

public mount core.math.foundations.self_recognition;
